original: Kristensson, Harry Elias Valdemar, komminister, Karlskrona, f. 27/ 11/07 i Osby, Krist. 1., av dir. Adolf K. o. Elisabet Eliasson. G. 39 m. Gul-le Ron, f. Anderzén. Barn: Kersti f. 35 (hustruns barn i tid. äkt.),’ Håkan 41. Stud:ex. i Lund 27, teol. fil. ex. 29, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov o. prästv._ f. Lunds stift 33. Tjg. s. pastorsadj. i Fjälkinge, v. pastor i Lin-deröd samt kyrkoadj. i Ronneby, förste kommin. i Karlskrona stadsförs, sed. 47. Red. f. ungd :tidn. Vår Krets.
translated: Kristensson, Harry Elias Valdemar, curate, Karlskrona, born on November 27, 1907 in Osby, son of director Adolf K. and Elisabet Eliasson. Married in 1939 to Gul-le Ron, born Anderzén. Children: Kersti, born in 1935 (wife's child from a previous marriage), Håkan, born in 1941. Graduated from Lund University in 1927, theology degree in 1929, ordained as a clergyman in the Lund diocese in 1933. Served as assistant pastor in Fjälkinge, vicar in Linderöd, and church assistant in Ronneby, first curate in Karlskrona city parish since 1947. Editor for the youth magazine Vår Krets.
